metadata.name: Resistance
metadata.description:
Sometimes we lose ourselves. Invisible walls envelop us like a water column. To continue living, you need to break through and take a breath of air.  
This collection is dedicated to our dreams and aspirations. Despite all circumstances, unbelief and doubts, you must follow for them. Against all odds. Per aspera ad astra.

Model: Natasha Afanaseva  
Mua&Hair: Anastasia Vavina  
Style: Natasha Khegay  
Art/Photo/Producer: Katrina Riri  
Assistants: Zlata Muhacheva, Bogdan Kolodin

___________  
"Resistance" 
1300x1700px, 300dpi
